{"tid":2113421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動POST】7/26 喧嘩遊行 - 沙田 荃灣 將軍澳","createTime":"2020-07-18T06:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T15:27:09.000Z","uid":282534,"like":25,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"adb40cdb1d50e54650c5403900e3e620f6f28042","tid":2113421,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F0i0pS6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF0i0pS6.jpg&h=88195ae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家好  又係我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自上次搞完佐敦靜默遊行之後 我地都見到大家其實好難忍得住口 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次就俾大家叫盡佢  有幾大聲就得幾大聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以 今次我地打算推行一個新既計劃<br />\n就是 <span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\"> 喧嘩遊行 </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n先講路線 然後係行動重點  請詳閱本次行動及守則<br />\n<br />\n三區各自路線<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"orange\">將軍澳</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cjvx0sa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcjvx0sa.jpg&h=a3a4e8fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由南豐商場出發 &gt; 連理街 &gt; 東港城 &gt; TKO Gateway I + II &gt; 解散<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"limegreen\">沙田</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVjVYdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVjVYdO.jpg&h=773f2995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由沙田中心出發 &gt; 沙田廣場 &gt; 新城市1期 &gt; 希爾頓 &gt; 新城市3期 &gt; 新城市1期 &gt; 解散<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"violet\">荃灣</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LFgQM7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLFgQM7a.jpg&h=fb359a3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YpaaM7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYpaaM7a.jpg&h=79ef1430&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由荃灣廣場出發 &gt; 荃新天地 &gt; 川龍街 &gt; 荃灣千色 &gt; 解散<br />\n<br />\n本次行動請<span class=\"red\">以安全性為最高度優先考慮項目</span><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">請大家配合一下規則上既玩法 <br />\n一致既行動會令大家安全性提高好多</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">九大行動重點 : </span>  </span></strong><br />\n1. 彩虹戰衣 , 另帶備其他彩虹後備衣服 行動完後請更換一次衣著<br />\n<span class=\"pink\">2. 3點前不集合 不停留 保持移動<br />\n3. 3點準時出發及起行<br />\n4. 3點半叫口號 限時3分鐘 有幾大聲得幾大聲  之後轉為靜默遊行</span><br />\n5. <strong><span class=\"red\">不屌狗 不撚狗 </span></strong> <br />\n6. 如果有狗係你面前封路 立即改變樓層/轉入內街/原地隱身 <br />\n7. 保持隨機應變策略  <br />\n8. <span class=\"limegreen\">提醒身旁中年人 佢地未必跟得上個玩法</span><br />\n9. 完成個人路線後請立即解散離開<br />\n<br />\n預計本次行動會有多次突發事故  <br />\n請按自己現場吸收到既資訊為最優先行動考慮因素 E.G : 走 / 繼續 / 暫避 / 隱形等<br />\n<br />\n另外 可以既話 請大家準備定 白色既MEMO紙<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v6y0p2s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv6y0p2s.jpg&h=a557751f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n可以係任何交通工具/地方 發揮作用  而且代替A4紙亦更為方便<br />\n<br />\n#2 為本期推薦文宣  請大家於路上不斷 Airdrop/Bluetooth 出去<br />\n#3 為一D廢話"},{"pid":"45c08122603c2021eb02fcfe82ad385046e7df56","tid":2113421,"uid":282534,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:10:31.000Z","msg":"#2<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J5no7qB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ5no7qB.jpg&h=d8669121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W8x8y5C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW8x8y5C.jpg&h=33055855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z7W1T5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz7W1T5D.jpg&h=cf657e96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sj52Dxj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSj52Dxj.jpg&h=5bf52f4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D7EKRSk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD7EKRSk.jpg&h=51b7ee25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/az465cm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faz465cm.jpg&h=b3ed0d76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yxo0qcn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYxo0qcn.jpg&h=f7bc76c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b7e82c7f034ab22e4eafa29ce0344ab0758ee34","tid":2113421,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:10:41.000Z","msg":"#3  <br />\n近期好多行動經常宣佈取消 <br />\n特別係須要狗方批准才可以行動既組織<br />\n以及好多行動開始重覆化  並可能一星期有幾次或以上<br />\n<br />\n經常取消行動 / 重覆單一性行動既行動 <br />\n好容易令大家對於吸收行動資訊出現疲態<br />\n繼而有行動都減少留意 / 無出席既意慾<br />\n<br />\n我地希望搞手行動係可以低調日常化  高調周末化<br />\n繼而令行動成效同顯著性更大<br />\n而且亦會令人更加留意黎緊有咩行動"},{"pid":"07c5c41d1b1d1dc397820567a95b1c130db97577","tid":2113421,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:11:50.000Z","msg":"漏左  呢個係 將軍澳全區天橋系統<br />\n<br />\n希望大家有用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SBifYyx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSBifYyx.jpg&h=b82b26b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b57a7875ce4d339438396b23152117dfe1d3020","tid":2113421,"uid":4798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:44:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e414ed60cc64f5cf5927463271ec8fb41a633a4","tid":2113421,"uid":270428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:49:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e0112406aef229d64ad91a0f449b7da316b48fe7","tid":2113421,"uid":10540,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:53:16.000Z","msg":"疫情已經多人確診，仲搞呢啲傻的嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":